content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 107.3 - Use of the term "New York State income tax return"
State Regulations

As used in this Subchapter, the term New York State
income tax return means any return required under article 22 of the Tax Law, unless the text clearly refers to a specific return required under such article
22 of the Tax Law. Notes
